trans-unit.source: The **Synchronization Service Manager** UI is used to configure more advanced aspects of the sync engine and to see the operational aspects of the service.
trans-unit.target: The **Synchronization Service Manager** UI is used to configure more advanced aspects of the sync engine and to see the operational aspects of the service.

trans-unit.source: You start the **Synchronization Service Manager** UI from the start menu.
trans-unit.target: You start the **Synchronization Service Manager** UI from the start menu.

trans-unit.source: It is named **Synchronization Service** and can be found in the **Azure AD Connect** group.
trans-unit.target: It is named **Synchronization Service** and can be found in the **Azure AD Connect** group.

trans-unit.source: Click on the links at the top of this topic to learn more about the different tabs in the UI.
trans-unit.target: Click on the links at the top of this topic to learn more about the different tabs in the UI.
